Package: chainlinkr
Title: Access Chainlink Price Feeds from R
Version: 0.0.0.1000
Authors@R: 
    person("Saw", "Simeon", 
           email = "saw.s@ku.th",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    chainlinkr provides a tidyverse-friendly interface to Chainlink Price Feeds.
    Data scientists, quantitative analysts, and researchers can retrieve real-time
    and historical decentralized price data (e.g., BTC/USD, ETH/USD, EUR/USD) from
    all Chainlink-supported networks directly in R â€” no blockchain knowledge or
    Web3 libraries required. Functions return tibbles and integrate seamlessly
    with ggplot2, dplyr, and the broader tidyverse ecosystem.
